{"tid":434592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中六生自殺前　託教師向同學交信","createTime":"2017-10-13T11:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T20:59:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb975457288cddc2717a2a0a4010d0b4aedde54","tid":434592,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171013/20181585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171013%2F20181585&d=msnUDYviB40nqSuaWU5zZNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8565ba12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171013%2F20181585&h=44230e22\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171013/20181585</a><br />\n<br />\n中六生自殺前　託教師向同學交信<br />\n<br />\n162,287<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171013/large/a0802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171013%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=7baea5de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油塘■警員撿走死者麥智宏（小圖）的書包。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】17歲中六生麥智宏墮樓亡，胞兄表示悲劇發生後，始知其弟智宏近日來有異樣，包括將他心愛物品打包送贈3位同學，前日又撰寫4封書信，交給教師後並請求於昨日轉交給3名同學。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉贈心愛物品<br />\n<br />\n胞兄稱，智宏較為內向，絕少吐露心事，不清楚他出事的原因。他稱，昨晨弟弟如常出門上學，其後在其房間發現一張字條及留下給家人的3,000元，他致電學校查詢，校方以未響鐘上堂為由未能確定他其弟去向，稍後再回電確定其弟的確無上學。<br />\n<br />\n家人其後報警，胞兄亦於網上尋人，但後來卻收到警方通知死訊。他回想連日發生的事，其實弟弟自殺有迹可尋，弟弟昨早出門時將個人最心愛的物品，如攝影機及背囊包成3份，原來他前天放學時交給教師4封信，一封給教師，並叮囑教師於昨日轉交3名同學，信件內容是交代個人物品送贈同學事宜。<br />\n<br />\n麥兄指智宏交信的行為異常，突然要教師轉遞多個同學，若能早察覺有異，或能及早制止悲劇，他亦承認作為家人對事件亦有很大責任。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉永明  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n學生自殺一日三宗　祖母離世父母婚變　小六男童跳樓亡<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n邵家臻斥漠視　林鄭：不用激動"},{"pid":"b2c86f43c71d24fae3ac88b2cc7046ed15272e8f","tid":434592,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bae72d628a8cad372f746e7db7e2b6663ae6170","tid":434592,"uid":2247,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:01:24.000Z","msg":"個老師有排訓唔著教"},{"pid":"0288258581e395496bae13e04e494baca9f68af6","tid":434592,"uid":34785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:10:58.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔都要跳，有d似陳家樂"},{"pid":"d389fbc63c8eb805614bbee84b06c2f50ccd0a47","tid":434592,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"個樣OK"},{"pid":"aaf266704019aba14e3e25ea52ff66935418fedc","tid":434592,"uid":142955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:12:48.000Z","msg":"唉 年輕人咁諗唔開呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723b9dcc7c77da291788bfa12d34926a5c554c78","tid":434592,"uid":136662,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:14:27.000Z","msg":"個哥對細佬一定好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d34bec86df6e2236c8c4e2e3081b830e53087b","tid":434592,"uid":140094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個哥對細佬一定好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n琴日比某d盲撚連登仔屌佢唔知有無虐待佢細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b9632b6fe92c1a0674285bc645338f165ede72","tid":434592,"uid":149634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:29:59.000Z","msg":"咁落去只會越死越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5467699c40bd2d434fc2d6929d0c098c6a160c31","tid":434592,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi